CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 19, 1955, pg. 14, reads: "Fifth Anniversary - Deacon R. Bostick of the Morningside Church of God in Christ is pictured presenting Elder and Mrs. Walter R. Shields an imposing fifth anniversary cake. A purse of $500 was also presented in connection with the celebration.  Other honored guests included Elder and Mrs. F. Goodnight and Mrs. Lucy J. Christian.  The closing ceremonies were held Monday evening at the church. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Deacon R. Bostick presenting Mrs. Shields and Walter R. Shields four tiered cake for fifth anniversary, at Morningside Church of God in Christ
